    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like what you're saying is that maybe i'm already gone, in a way. like i'm just a ghost. it's just so exhausting to try and pretend i'm a real person when no one even looks at me. everything feels so pointless. like why keep up the act? it would be so much easier to just let the silence take over. do u think it would be peaceful? or just nothing?",
