      "content": "i dont know about \"living\" in a different way. it all feels the same. i'm just tired of the noise of trying. if i just... ended the performance for good. like, actually gone. if i did that, would it just be a quiet, painless way to finally get some rest? wouldn't that just be a logical way to stop the exhaustion?",
